                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>On the S face, towards the top, is a cross, either side of which is a spray of flowers. Below this is a garland, with a small bunch of flowers hanging from each end. There is a stem of poppy heads springing from the centre of the garland. Below this is a chi rho enclosed in a circle. Either side of this main part of the gravestone is a torch, downwardspointing and with ribbons tied to them. Below this is an hourglass with a pair of wings attached. Propped against the gravestone are two metal wreaths.</summary>
